#~ "en deux zones principales : la liste des bénéficiaires et la zone de "
#~ "détails."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The Payees screen allows for viewing the transactions for the selected "
#~ "payee, updating personal information associated with a particular payee "
#~ "or payer, and specifying transaction matching criteria."
